<Seo Canonical="/docs/helpers/enums/validation" Title="Blazorise Validation Enums - Modes and Status" Description="Validation enums define when validation runs and how results are represented. Learn ValidationMode and ValidationStatus values." />

<DocsPageTitle>
    Enums: Validation
</DocsPageTitle>

<DocsPageLead>
    Control when validation runs and how results are represented.
</DocsPageLead>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    Validation enums let you choose automatic or manual validation and interpret the outcome consistently.
</DocsPageParagraph>

<DocsPageSubtitle>
    How it works
</DocsPageSubtitle>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    Use <Code>ValidationMode</Code> to decide when validation executes and <Code>ValidationStatus</Code> to represent outcomes.
</DocsPageParagraph>

<DocsPageSubtitle>
    Examples
</DocsPageSubtitle>

<UnorderedList>
    <UnorderedListItem><Code>ValidationMode.Auto</Code> to validate on each input change.</UnorderedListItem>
    <UnorderedListItem><Code>ValidationMode.Manual</Code> to validate on submit.</UnorderedListItem>
    <UnorderedListItem><Code>ValidationStatus.Error</Code> to flag failed validation.</UnorderedListItem>
</UnorderedList>

<DocsPageSubtitle>
    Reference
</DocsPageSubtitle>

<DocsPageSection>
    <DocsPageSectionHeader Title="ValidationMode">
        <Paragraph>Defines the validation execution mode.</Paragraph>
        <UnorderedList>
            <UnorderedListItem><Code>ValidationMode.Auto</Code> Validation will execute on every input change.</UnorderedListItem>
            <UnorderedListItem><Code>ValidationMode.Manual</Code> Validation will run only when explicitly called.</UnorderedListItem>
        </UnorderedList>
    </DocsPageSectionHeader>
</DocsPageSection>

<DocsPageSection>
    <DocsPageSectionHeader Title="ValidationStatus">
        <Paragraph>Defines the validation results.</Paragraph>
        <UnorderedList>
            <UnorderedListItem><Code>ValidationStatus.None</Code> No validation.</UnorderedListItem>
            <UnorderedListItem><Code>ValidationStatus.Success</Code> Validation has passed the check.</UnorderedListItem>
            <UnorderedListItem><Code>ValidationStatus.Error</Code> Validation has failed.</UnorderedListItem>
        </UnorderedList>
    </DocsPageSectionHeader>
</DocsPageSection>